        <updateDate>2019-09-20T10:30:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Solar Energy Research and Development Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to carry out a grant program to research, develop, and evaluate&nbsp;solar energy technologies and systems.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>07</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2020-09-11</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Reported to House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-12-10T15:19:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Solar Energy Research and Development Act of 2019</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to carry out a program to award grants or enter into contracts and cooperative agreements to research, develop, and evaluate&nbsp;solar energy technologies and systems. The program replaces several existing programs concerning solar research and development.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
